e":"The most commented videos have all more than 4.500 likes, with the max of nearly 11.000 likes. Nine of the 10 most watched videos are from the category \"morning yoga\". Seven of the videos are part of a Yoga challenge series. The video lenght are all under 20 minutes.\n\nVideos with more engagement seems to be videos that are shorter, with a morning thme and part of a challenge.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**List of yoga subjects/styles in the dataset**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"yoga_subjects <- unique(yoga$yogaSubject)\n\nprint(yoga_subjects)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-04-28T13:12:17.571737Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-04-28T13:12:17.573999Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-04-28T13:12:17.596752Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":27,"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":" [1] \"Morning Yoga\"         \"Zodiac yoga\"          \"Intermediate Yoga\"   \n [4] \"Yin Yoga\"             \"Vinyasa Flow Yoga\"    \"Other\"               \n [7] \"Beginner Yoga\"        \"Challenge\"            \"Tutorial\"            \n[10] \"Yoga Quotes\"          \"Power Yoga\"           \"Meditation\"          \n[13] \"Evening/Bedtime Yoga\" \"Advanced Yoga\"        \"Chakra Yoga\"         \n","output_type":"stream"}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"yoga_subject_counts_df <- as.data.frame(table(yoga$yogaSubject))\n\ncolnames(yoga_subject_counts_df) <- c(\"yogaSubject\", \"counts\")\n\nyoga_subject_counts_df <- yoga_subject_counts_df[order(-yoga_subject_counts_df$counts), ]\n\nprint(yoga_subject_counts_df)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-04-28T13:12:41.709236Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-04-28T13:12:41.711133Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-04-28T13:12:41.742498Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":28,"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"            yogaSubject counts\n8          Morning Yoga    201\n12    Vinyasa Flow Yoga    150\n13             Yin Yoga     97\n2         Beginner Yoga     66\n9              